ft class=m><span class=title>   Re: Mana Preservaction Items and Mod 2.0</span><hr size=1> Hmmm does that mean our summoned earring and a mana preservation item stack...I will guess they don't ! =)<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uzyphyr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zyphyr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 431<br> <font color=#333333>(7/30/02 5:03:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=851.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Mana Preservaction Items and Mod 2.0</span><hr size=1> Nope... if 2 Foci would give the same effect to a spell only the greater of the two work.<br>
<br>
The earring has a larger savings than a Mana preservation item, so....<br>
<br>
If you cast a nuke, the earing will trigger<br>
If you cast any other spell (except CH), the MP item is what triggers.<br>
If you cast CH, neither triggers.<br>
<br>
<br>
(note: CH info included only to make the information as generic as possible) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=wyndor>Wyndor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#333333>(7/30/02 5:53:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=851.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Mana Preservaction Items and Mod 2.0</span><hr size=1> How do you tell which effect is better?  Our 54 bauble or mana preservation 3? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/utziarius.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tziarius</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 30<br> <font color=#333333>(7/31/02 5:57:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=851.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Mana Preservaction Items and Mod 2.0</span><hr size=1> Which ever goes off with the spell is the better one for that spell.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ulothharlomax.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lothhar Lomax</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_greenspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#333333>(8/2/02 2:26:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=851.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://loomis.urx.com/loomis/thumbloth.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Mana Preservaction Items and Mod 2.0</span><hr size=1> 54 bauble activiates and Obulus Death Shroud doesn't for nukes.<br>
<br>
Enshrouded Veil activiates and ODS doesn't for pets.<br>
<br>
Everything else ODS activates.<br>
<br>
