</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=wyndor>Wyndor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#333333>(8/2/02 5:17:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=851.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   ABC 123's</span><hr size=1> I've heard the 1, 2, &amp; 3 on the focus items determine the lvls of the spells that they work on.  Is this true or do they work on all spells just a different percentage? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uzyphyr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zyphyr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 440<br> <font color=#333333>(8/2/02 5:52:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=851.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Mana Preservaction Items and Mod 2.0</span><hr size=1> Level 1 foci work on spells level 1-20<br>
Level 2 foci work on spells level 1-44<br>
Level 3 foci work on all spell levels<br>
<br>
The magnatude of the effect is constant. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ulimpylionbait.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LimpyLionBait</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 128<br> <font color=#333333>(8/2/02 5:55:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=851.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: ABC 123's</span><hr size=1> You are correct - for instance the Black Alloy Medallion has the effect Mana Preservation II, which affects all spells from level 1 to 44.<br>
<br>
Mana Preservation I works on spells level 1 to 20 or 22 I think, and MP III works on all spells level 1 to 60.<br>
<br>
I still keep a BA medallion on me even at level 53, as it saves mana when making mod rods (Mod rod 1, not version 2 <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ), using my 44 magic based nuke, casting arch shielding, summoning flight rings / waterstones / staves / bag'o'plate for pets, lots of spells. I don't wear it all the time  mind you, just when I'd get enough of a mana savings to make it worth using. <br>
<br>
Anyone else still using one at 50+? or am I the lone crazy person...<br>
<br>
Ooh a question - does shield of the arch magi stack with arch shielding?<br>
<br>
Thanks -Limpy <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uvilephire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vilephire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 111<br> <font color=#333333>(8/2/02 9:23:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=851.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: ABC 123's</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Ooh a question - does shield of the arch magi stack with arch shielding?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
If you mean 'Shield of the Magi' then no, it doesn't stack with Arch Shielding. They are part of the same line of buffs, so the greater one will take effect. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ulimpylionbait.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LimpyLionBait</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 129<br> <font color=#333333>(8/3/02 8:52:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=851.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: ABC 123's</span><hr size=1> okies thank you! <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showPrevMessage?topicID=851.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showNextMessage?topicID=851.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=851.topic&index=12><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.threadControl?topicID=851.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=851.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=851.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </t